//
// Conventions:
// Unit      | Range         | Notes
// :-------- |:-------------:|:-----
// timestamp | >= 0          | Unix timestamp, number of seconds since 1970/01/01 00:00:00 UTC
// year      | 1970 ... 2345 |
// month     | 1 ... 12      |
// day       | 1 ... 31      |
// hour      | 0 ... 23      |
// minute    | 0 ... 59      |
